        <Parent_String>tone (color effect) [300056173], color-related effects [300209700], color (perceived attribute) [300056130], color and color-related phenomena [300209420], Color (hierarchy name) [300131647], Physical Attributes Facet [300264087]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
